readable.content: A small dog and a large dog carrying a stick in its mouth run outside . A smaller white dog is trying to get a hold of a stick that a bigger tri-colored dog has in its mouth . The little white dog is trying to bite onto the stick that the black dog is carrying . Two dogs run and play with a brown stick . two dogs run for a stick .
